<div class="title">A Mighty Rash</div>
<div class="substance">Kava & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Dr+B&Exact=1">Dr B</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Dr B. "A Mighty Rash: An Experience with Kava & Alcohol (exp61736)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 10, 2010. erowid.org/exp/61736</div>

